{"tid":1690292,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"曱甴太上皇習仲勛（甴仲勛）：廣東獨立","createTime":"2019-11-03T08:54:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-31T20:34:05.000Z","uid":308492,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"21e6cb7474c5e24070fa8c90e3ad97bf01e316be","tid":1690292,"uid":308492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T08:54:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>習仲勛（甴仲勛）先係曱甴王，早過李嘉誠！</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://img2.secretchina.com/pic/2017/11-6/p2025591a296030099-ss.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg2.secretchina.com%2Fpic%2F2017%2F11-6%2Fp2025591a296030099-ss.jpg&h=d9a52d0d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n   在向中央政治局常委匯報時，習仲勳陳述了廣東獨特的發展優勢，大膽地提出自己的意見:&ldquo;現在中央的權力過於集中，地方上感到事情很難辦。沒有權，辦事很難。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n  主持會議的華國鋒問:&ldquo;仲勳同志，你們廣東究竟想要什麽權？&rdquo;會場氣氛緊張起來。<br />\n<br />\n  習仲勳面對中央最高負責人，他感覺到了決定廣東命運的緊要關頭。盡管他提出的設想可能不合某些領導人的口味，但廣東已經沒有退路。<br />\n<br />\n  習仲勳終於將底牌拋了出去:&ldquo;我代表省委，請求中央允許在毗鄰港澳邊界的深圳、珠海與重要的僑鄉汕頭市各劃出一塊地方，搞貿易合作區。&rdquo;最後，他索性把話說痛快。他語出驚人地說出一句振聾發聵的話:&ldquo;<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">如果廣東是一個獨立的國家，可能幾年就搞上去了，但是在現在的體制下，就不容易上去。</span></strong></span>&rdquo;這種針對束縛生產力發展僵化體制的大膽&ldquo;出格言詞&rdquo;，別人都不會說、不敢說或者不能說，只有長期在中央和西北工作，此刻又作為廣東當家人的習仲勳敢說。他無所畏懼地坦蕩直言，令當時頭腦仍未轉過彎來的人們吃了一驚。<br />\n<br />\n  習仲勳趁熱打鐵繼續說:&ldquo;<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">廣東希望中央給個新的體制和政策，這樣廣東幾年就能搞上去。廣東是一個大省，等於周邊地區的一個甚至幾個國家呀，但現在省的地方機動權太小了，國家和中央部門統得過死，不利於國民經濟發展。</span></strong></span>我們希望，中央給點權，讓廣東先走一步，放手幹。這樣做，對地方有利，對中央也有利呀。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\nSource：<br />\n品蔥 廣東省委第一書記，粵獨先驅習仲勛<br />\n<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/7235\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpincong.rocks%2Farticle%2F7235&d=AnzAvEp6rraOVT5%2FQxAiQbJtyMJyNHaGyUrVEdcKl1A%3D&h=8d67edd6\" target=\"_blank\">https://pincong.rocks/article/7235</a><br />\n人民日報 習仲勳：為改革開放殺出一條血路<br />\n<a href=\"http://cpc.people.com.cn/GB/85037/8599316.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcpc.people.com.cn%2FGB%2F85037%2F8599316.html&d=AnzAvEp6rraOVT5%2FQxAiQbJtyMJyNHaGyUrVEdcKl1A%3D&h=51832d03\" target=\"_blank\">http://cpc.people.com.cn/GB/85037/8599316.html</a><br />\n<br />\n關鍵字 曱甴平 曱近平 甴近平 習近平 習仲勛 甴仲勛 曱仲勛"},{"pid":"f97cc43dce05aa6fc5dbad6917850532ea44f530","tid":1690292,"uid":306576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T08:59:14.000Z","msg":"甴習平!"},{"pid":"33dda0c462537fec6858025f0a67d59daf209d54","tid":1690292,"uid":306576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f97cc43dce05aa6fc5dbad6917850532ea44f530","tid":1690292,"uid":306576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T08:59:14.000Z","msg":"甴習平!"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T08:59:39.000Z","msg":"*甴近平!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b46edba91ce9114c8cc3c3752a350d8d28de170","tid":1690292,"uid":329448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"21e6cb7474c5e24070fa8c90e3ad97bf01e316be","tid":1690292,"uid":308492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T08:54:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>習仲勛（甴仲勛）先係曱甴王，早過李嘉誠！</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://img2.secretchina.com/pic/2017/11-6/p2025591a296030099-ss.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg2.secretchina.com%2Fpic%2F2017%2F11-6%2Fp2025591a296030099-ss.jpg&h=d9a52d0d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n   在向中央政治局常委匯報時，習仲勳陳述了廣東獨特的發展優勢，大膽地提出自己的意見:&ldquo;現在中央的權力過於集中，地方上感到事情很難辦。沒有權，辦事很難。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n  主持會議的華國鋒問:&ldquo;仲勳同志，你們廣東究竟想要什麽權？&rdquo;會場氣氛緊張起來。<br />\n<br />\n  習仲勳面對中央最高負責人，他感覺到了決定廣東命運的緊要關頭。盡管他提出的設想可能不合某些領導人的口味，但廣東已經沒有退路。<br />\n<br />\n  習仲勳終於將底牌拋了出去:&ldquo;我代表省委，請求中央允許在毗鄰港澳邊界的深圳、珠海與重要的僑鄉汕頭市各劃出一塊地方，搞貿易合作區。&rdquo;最後，他索性把話說痛快。他語出驚人地說出一句振聾發聵的話:&ldquo;<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">如果廣東是一個獨立的國家，可能幾年就搞上去了，但是在現在的體制下，就不容易上去。</span></strong></span>&rdquo;這種針對束縛生產力發展僵化體制的大膽&ldquo;出格言詞&rdquo;，別人都不會說、不敢說或者不能說，只有長期在中央和西北工作，此刻又作為廣東當家人的習仲勳敢說。他無所畏懼地坦蕩直言，令當時頭腦仍未轉過彎來的人們吃了一驚。<br />\n<br />\n  習仲勳趁熱打鐵繼續說:&ldquo;<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">廣東希望中央給個新的體制和政策，這樣廣東幾年就能搞上去。廣東是一個大省，等於周邊地區的一個甚至幾個國家呀，但現在省的地方機動權太小了，國家和中央部門統得過死，不利於國民經濟發展。</span></strong></span>我們希望，中央給點權，讓廣東先走一步，放手幹。這樣做，對地方有利，對中央也有利呀。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\nSource：<br />\n品蔥 廣東省委第一書記，粵獨先驅習仲勛<br />\n<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/7235\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpincong.rocks%2Farticle%2F7235&d=AnzAvEp6rraOVT5%2FQxAiQbJtyMJyNHaGyUrVEdcKl1A%3D&h=8d67edd6\" target=\"_blank\">https://pincong.rocks/article/7235</a><br />\n人民日報 習仲勳：為改革開放殺出一條血路<br />\n<a href=\"http://cpc.people.com.cn/GB/85037/8599316.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcpc.people.com.cn%2FGB%2F85037%2F8599316.html&d=AnzAvEp6rraOVT5%2FQxAiQbJtyMJyNHaGyUrVEdcKl1A%3D&h=51832d03\" target=\"_blank\">http://cpc.people.com.cn/GB/85037/8599316.html</a><br />\n<br />\n關鍵字 曱甴平 曱近平 甴近平 習近平 習仲勛 甴仲勛 曱仲勛"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T08:59:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/qjwVcuCrmLo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FqjwVcuCrmLo&d=AnzAvEp6rraOVT5%2FQxAiQbJtyMJyNHaGyUrVEdcKl1A%3D&h=e75441e6\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/qjwVcuCrmLo</a>"},{"pid":"9bbb711ec326aa78d7f8033714208d157a41c51b","tid":1690292,"uid":19437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T09:02:54.000Z","msg":"讓香港先走一步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cabf5785606a424a106b61023598210ccecc430c","tid":1690292,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T09:06:40.000Z","msg":"不肖子：甴維尼"},{"pid":"fd187dc164602b57f7dc3c622e909fa23fff69b3","tid":1690292,"uid":308492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cabf5785606a424a106b61023598210ccecc430c","tid":1690292,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T09:06:40.000Z","msg":"不肖子：甴維尼"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T09:09:46.000Z","msg":"佢老豆識得放權地方搞經濟<br />\n佢個不孝子竟然開倒車加強中央集權"},{"pid":"5dc3fc796b944ab43c7f80752acf7acc04b649e7","tid":1690292,"uid":36134,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T10:06:19.000Z","msg":"當年好多人都失算,估錯晒習近平<br />\n以為佢老豆係開明派,仲要比毛魔鬥死左<br />\n斷估佢都唔會係極左路線<br />\n會繼續行鄧小平,胡錦濤條路<br />\n點知係佢個腦原來塞滿晒毛魔主義,紅色極左思想"},{"pid":"97b27dfacd2a9c5d90b69232d9a946384dada12a","tid":1690292,"uid":306576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T20:34:05.000Z","msg":"樓豬連登知名5毛，B.L.O.C.K<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}